snippet.title: Amber Liu Reads Thirst Tweets
snippet.description:
Fresh off the release of her newest album "y?", Amber Liu stopped by to read the internet's thirstiest tweets about herself, and to encourage y’all thirsty people to do more wholesome activities. Absolutely no stepping on anyone... except maybe if it’s for charity. #AmberLiu #Buzzfeed #ThirstTweets

Credits: https://www.buzzfeed.com/bfmp/videos/131602
